-- Orbit seed users — 40 fake AFE interns spread across Amazon corporate hubs.
-- Run AFTER supabase-schema.sql, in the Supabase SQL Editor.
-- Idempotent: deterministic UUIDs + ON CONFLICT means re-running is safe.
-- These are fake demo profiles (sample LinkedIn handles, @example.com emails).

